hexagon-cross-toolchain (0.1.0~20260311) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial packaging of Hexagon cross-compilation sysroot.
  * Builds linux headers, musl, compiler-rt builtins, libc++, and picolibc
    using the system clang-21/lld-21.
  * Seven binary packages following Debian cross-toolchain conventions.

